{"tid":4062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【血滴子】佛山餐廳吊扇從天而降 婦人臉部割傷","createTime":"2016-11-26T11:19:13.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T14:21:32.000Z","uid":122,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d90c362ad554497344d4fbe57bff836a9847ff60","tid":4062,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T11:19:13.000Z","msg":"<strong>【巧驚驚】佛山餐廳吊扇從天而降 婦人臉部割傷</strong><br />\n<br />\n2016-11-26 18:26:00 HKT<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佛山市襌城區的鄧姓女子，近日公開始在一間餐廳食飯「中頭獎」的經歷。她在一間餐廳用餐時，天花板的吊扇突然從天而降，擊中她的臉部，雖然目前傷口已經癒合，但她與餐廳東主仍未談妥賠償問題。<br />\n<br />\n鄧女在上月14日凌晨，然與多名友人到當地一間海鮮粥餐廳用餐，由於他們人數多，餐廳安排她們到沒有冷氣、只有吊扇的露台用餐。食到半路，吊扇突然「嘭」一聲跌下來，鄧女感到臉上「好像有水流下來」，用手一按全都是血。<br />\n<br />\n鄧女到醫院急救，醫生稱她的傷口長2厘米、深0.5厘米，要縫5針。鄧女的朋友在現場拍到照片顯示，吊扇上佈滿灰塵，扇葉邊緣已經生鏽，似乎已經是使用多年。<br />\n<br />\n鄧女稱，海鮮粥餐廳東主願意負醫療費用，但鄧女稱受傷後無法工作，同時要祛疤手術，要求3萬元人民幣賠償，但東主卻認為她要求太多，不能接受。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb514fc90729ae1bf8165f64b65c022683e5bb9c","tid":4062,"uid":15972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T11:35:40.000Z","msg":"真係血滴子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34827d7d1d6d7f5adc54575c9ad6dd88bf28420e","tid":4062,"uid":23150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T11:37:47.000Z","msg":"以前上堂都好驚跌落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ed0b095783eccec097e1769336f9884640b813b","tid":4062,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T11:43:44.000Z","msg":"強國一日幾單啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca5c21749d76de84dadb21bf4ffedb5a60a24564","tid":4062,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T11:46:06.000Z","msg":"咁都冇斷頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc84e7e47eaf2aec29cb1c8eefcb7c9b37a69a14","tid":4062,"uid":24441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T13:03:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZfJW61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZfJW61.jpg&h=e4620584&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1a066f6ac217637b0050fc0f0e95211ba03cebf","tid":4062,"uid":3128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T13:11:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe795145abb1536a74e2ed4391b14d07f766839","tid":4062,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}